Phyllis Coates https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phyllis_Coates 0 Phyllis Coates (born Gypsie Ann Evarts Stell; January 15, 1927) is an American actress. She is best known for her portrayal of reporter Lois Lane in the 1951 film Superman and the Mole Men and in the first season of the television series Adventures of Superman.
